{"word":"ἐπονομάζω","slug":"ἐπονομάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπονομάζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to give a surname: to name</i> or <i>call</i> so and so, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be named</i>, <el>ἀπό τινος</el> or <el>τινος</el> <i>after</i> one, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:— <i>to be surnamed</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to pronounce</i> a name, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}